sources.title: Rock River Renegades
sources.description: Having trouble with outlaws, Marshal Graham (Kermit Maynard) sends for his friends the Range Busters. Newspaper editor Ross (Christine McIntyre), dissatisfied with Graham, forms a vigilante committee and puts Jim Dawson (Weldon Heyburn) in charge not knowing he is the leader of the outlaw gang. Dawson then has his men frame Crash (Ray Corrigan) and Dusty (John King) for robbery and murder and then has them set out to lynch the two.
